...

Perhaps,

Fuck it, I want to live.

Let me come with you.

PC: Ha! Why not. [[success6]]

No. [[failure5]]


:: 3.1.2 {"position":"700,4800","size":"100,100"}
PC: Flattery won't save you here

M: That wasn't the intention,

But if it were to work...

I may be so bold to comment on your capabilities,

Perhaps the very real possibility of you making it out of here alive.

What are you trying to say? [[3.1.2.1]]

I'm done playing around. [[failure23]]


:: 3.1.2.1 {"position":"900,4900","size":"100,100"}
